LAMMPS (22 Jul 2025 - Update 1)
units real
atom_style full
boundary p p p

pair_style lj/cut/tip4p/long 1 2 1 1 0.1577 9.5

bond_style zero
angle_style zero
pair_modify tail yes

read_data tip4p-ice-225K.data
Reading data file ...
  orthogonal box = (-25 -25 -25) to (25 25 25)
  2 by 4 by 7 MPI processor grid
